topic.title: libp2p -A modular and extensible networking stack for p2p

2_1APx2pf1wNGFz4mWCN2sFzrtTGzrLKZUQ2.body:
not very reliable last time i checked.
someday soon it will work better.
there is active development AFIK.
reliance on pubs make it more centralized.
documentation is scarce but occasionally available. Impressive given what it is.
cool community but could diversify it's identity IMO.
not very supportive of privacy.
node.js seems to be a central theme.
very young and early in development yet it truly works!(more or less).
